The,service,provides,real,time,information,about,status,and,scheduling,within,the,Utah,Transit,Authority,systems,Information,covers,multiple,transit,options,including,buses,and,commuter,trains,Its,data,structure,is,an,implementation,of,the,SIRI,Service,Interface,for,Real,Time,Information,standard,for,consistency,with,other,providers,of,similar,data,API,methods,support,monitoring,of,a,specific,vehicle,either,bus,or,train,or,monitoring,service,along,a,specified,route,or,at,a,particular,stop,Methods,also,can,provide,the,closest,transit,stop,to,a,location,specified,as,latitude,and,longitude